scripts.build: mkdir -p lib; protoc -I ${PROTOLOC:-$GOPATH/src/github.com/grpc-ecosystem/grpc-gateway}/third_party/googleapis -I /usr/lib/protoc/include --swagger_out=logtostderr=true:. -I${PROTOLOC:-..} ${PROTOLOC:-..}/*.proto && mv *.swagger.json lib && for f in $(ls lib/*.swagger.json); do yarn dtsgen -o ${f%.swagger.json}.dt.ts $f; done
